{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "本章《第四回 黑风双煞》以“完颜洪熙笑道：\"好，再打他个痛快。\"蒙古兵前哨报来：\"王罕亲自前来迎接大金国两位太子。”开篇，围绕主要人物的行踪、冲突和江湖牵连展开。中段写到“\"叫道：\"大哥，你知道谁叫杨康么？\"”，推动人物关系和武功线索变化；后段转向“\"朱聪道：\"是啊，听说是给桃花岛主革逐出门了。这两人心狠手辣，武功高强，行事又十分机灵，当真神出鬼没。”，并以“她中了大哥的毒菱，多半这时已毒发身死。且把孩子先送回家去，咱们有伤的先服药养伤，然后三弟、六弟、七妹你们三人”收束，为后续章节继续埋下因果。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "完颜洪熙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，再打他个痛快。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王罕笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王罕笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完颜洪烈道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "桑昆脸现怒色，把金杯在木案上重重一碰。铁木真忙道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_yan_hong_lie",
      "speaker_name": "完颜洪烈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四杰？是那几位呀？我倒想见见。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁木真道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完颜洪烈道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞧在义父脸上，我便再让桑昆一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "桑昆喝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你回来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "桑昆道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王罕喝道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完颜洪熙却一心想瞧热闹，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "随从呈上了一大壶酒。铁木真提了酒壶，大声说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "众兵将叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "众兵叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁木真大声道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "众人一楞，随即会意，知是铁木真升了哲别的职位，欢呼叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_ji_si_han",
      "speaker_name": "铁木真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拿我的头盔来！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "桑昆微微一笑，低声道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纵声叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四杰一听，个个大怒，均想：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁木真也极不乐意，大声道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "桑昆哈哈大笑，说道：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完颜洪熙大喜，从手指上除下一个鲜红 的宝石戒指，投在地下，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_ji_si_han",
      "speaker_name": "铁木真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "桑昆兄弟，你赢啦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_lei",
      "speaker_name": "拖雷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂，兔子是我射死的，你拿去干么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拖雷道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拖雷道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_lei",
      "speaker_name": "拖雷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那孩子更加凶了，伸手在拖雷肩头一推，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_lei",
      "speaker_name": "拖雷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我爹爹是铁木真。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "都史道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拖了郭靖的手转身就逃。都史怒叫：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纵马走近，见是七八个大孩子欺侮两个小孩，两个小的给按在地下，都已给打得鼻青口肿，喝道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "马的人骂",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子这样横，快放手！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "一个女子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三哥，别管闲事，走吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_zhen_e",
      "speaker_name": "柯镇恶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "赶道吧，别等前面市集散了，可问不到人啦！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拖雷满脸怒容，摇头不答。都史道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁敢上来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "起了据为己有之念，笑吟吟的下马，说道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "笑弥陀张阿生笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "闹市侠隐全金发道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看了不住口的啧啧称赏，见剑柄上刻着",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两字，心中一楞：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_zhen_e",
      "speaker_name": "柯镇恶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_zhen_e",
      "speaker_name": "柯镇恶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没听说过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱聪笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_xiao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "韩小莹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们回去问问那小孩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_lei",
      "speaker_name": "拖雷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，明天再打。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_cong",
      "speaker_name": "朱聪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还我！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖伸袖子一擦鼻中仍在流下来的鲜血，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱聪问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_quan_jin_fa",
      "speaker_name": "全金发",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你姓杨么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_cong",
      "speaker_name": "朱聪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨康是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_lei",
      "speaker_name": "拖雷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖安答，回去罢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 391,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柯镇恶大喜，急问：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柯镇恶搔头问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柯镇恶听他语气中似含敌意，叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "韩小莹跳下马来，温言道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_xiao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "韩小莹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "韩小莹问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖咬牙切齿的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啸哥",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 411
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭大哥",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 411
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段天德",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_xiao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "韩小莹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小兄弟，咱们坐下来慢慢说话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要回去啦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 429,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_cong",
      "speaker_name": "朱聪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三弟，莫莽撞。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 437,
      "line_end": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "喝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "钻进去！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 447,
      "line_end": 447
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从怀中摸出一块汗巾，交给拖雷，向柯镇恶一指，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 455,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拖雷依言把汗巾缚在柯镇恶眼上，笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
